                            <comment id="15953647" author="jmaron" created="Mon, 3 Apr 2017 15:12:16 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I am running a spark job and, when instantiating a HiveContext, I see that the client creates a local derby-based metastore.  Is this the intent for client processes?  I don&apos;t understand the necessity for a client process to create a metastore instance rather than leverage the remote metastore server.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
